  "response": "Finding the best earphones under \u20b9500 in India with good sound quality can be challenging given the budget constraints, but here are some of the popular options that you might consider:\n\n1. **boAt BassHeads 100**: Known for its powerful bass and clear sound quality, these earphones come with an in-line microphone for hands-free communication and a lightweight design.\n\n2. **Mi Earphones Basic**: These earphones from Xiaomi offer good audio quality and bass response, along with an in-line microphone and a sleek design.\n\n3. **Realme Buds 2**: Realme Buds 2 is a popular choice in this price range with good sound quality, deep bass, and a built-in mic. Though sometimes slightly above the \u20b9500 mark during sales, they can be found within the budget.\n\n4. **Infinity (JBL) Zip 100**: Infinity is a sub-brand of JBL that provides decent sound quality and comfort. The Zip 100 earphones come with a mic and offer balanced sound.\n\n5. **Philips SHE1505**: These earphones from Philips offer decent sound quality, lightweight design, and come with an in-line microphone.\n\nIt's crucial to check for the latest reviews and prices online, as these can fluctuate, and new models may become available. Make sure to verify specifications and read user reviews to ensure the product meets your sound quality expectations.",
